MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data) WHERE (t.trade.name == '零售' OR t.trade.name == '航空航天') AND td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-10') RETURN t.trade.name, td.trade_data.`date`, td.trade_data.`date`, td.trade_data.opening_price, td.trade_data.minimum_price, td.trade_data.maximum_price
LIMIT 50;
candidates:

WHERE ( indus.industry.name == "零售" OR indus.industry.name == "航空航天" ) AND td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-10') 
RETURN s.stock
LIMIT 50

MATCH (t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data) WHERE (t.trade.name == '运输和物流' OR t.trade.name == '银行') AND td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-10') RETURN t.trade.name, td.trade_data.`date`, td.trade_data.opening_price, td.trade_data.closing_price
LIMIT 50;
candidates:

WHERE td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-10') AND ( indus.industry.name == "运输" OR indus.industry.name == "物流" ) 
RETURN s.stock
LIMIT 50

MATCH (indus:industry)<-[a:associate]-(s:stock)-[bt:belong_to]->(t:trade)-[htd:has_trade_data]->(td:trade_data)
WHERE ( indus.industry.name == "运输" OR indus.industry.name == "物流" ) AND td.trade_data.`date` == date('2023-11-10') 
RETURN s.stock
LIMIT 50

LIMIT 50;

RETURN td.trade_data.minimum_price,td.trade_data.opening_price,indus.industry.name,td.trade_data.closing_price
